#~ msgid ""
#~ "<guilabel>SEP Parameters</guilabel>: This sets the SEP parameter profile "
#~ "appropriate for the scope type attached in the selected Optical Train. By "
#~ "hovering the mouse over this label you can see in the tooltip what values "
#~ "Focus Advisor is recommending."
